resources.string: Material is the metaphor Motion respects and reinforces the user as the prime mover. Primary user actions are inflection points that initiate motion, transforming the whole design All action takes place in a single environment. Objects are presented to the user without breaking the continuity of experience even as they transform and reorganize .
